sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant API as Chat API
    participant Conv as Conversation Service
    participant Retrieval as Retrieval Engine
    participant Prompt as Prompt Assembly
    participant LLM as Chat Provider
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Feedback as Feedback API

    User->>API: POST /api/projects/{project_id}/chat/messages
    API->>Conv: create or validate conversation(project_id)
    Conv->>DB: insert user message
    API->>Retrieval: retrieve(project_id, query, options)
    Retrieval->>DB: project-scoped chunk search
    Retrieval-->>API: chunks + retrieval_log_id

    alt no usable context
        API->>DB: insert assistant refusal message
        API-->>User: no-answer response
    else context available
        API->>Prompt: build messages and citation map
        Prompt-->>API: provider messages
        API->>LLM: generate answer
        LLM-->>API: answer text + model metadata
        API->>DB: insert assistant message
        API->>DB: insert message_citations linked to chunks
        API-->>User: answer + citations
    end

    User->>Feedback: POST /api/projects/{project_id}/feedback
    Feedback->>DB: validate assistant message belongs to project_id
    Feedback->>DB: insert feedback rating
    Feedback-->>User: feedback record
